15:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda ortiqcha ish oshirilgan miqdorda to'lanadi: dastlabki 2 soat — oddiy soatlik stavkadan 1,5 baravarda, har keyingi soat — 2 baravarda. Dam olish va bayram kunlaridagi ish 2 baravarda to'lanadi yoki boshqa dam olish kuni bilan qoplanadi (xodimning tanloviga ko'ra). O'zbekistonda standart ish haftasi — 40 soat (5 kun 8 soatdan)."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Ortiqcha ishning maksimal davomiyligi Mehnat kodeksi bilan qat'iy cheklangan: ketma-ket 2 kun uchun 4 soatdan ko'p emas va yiliga 120 soatdan ko'p emas. Ortiqcha ishga jalb qilish faqat xodimning yozma roziligi bilan ruxsat etiladi. Taqiqlangan: homilador ayollar, 18 yoshgacha xodimlar, nogironlar (ularning yozma roziligi va tibbiy xulosasiz)."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash uchun soatlik stavka aniqlanadi: vaqtbay to'lovda — okladni oydagi ish soatlari soniga bo'lish (odatda 168 soat); ishbayda — o'rtacha kunlik ishlab chiqarishni 8 soatga bo'lish. Tungi ish (22:00 dan 06:00 gacha) soatlik stavkaning kamida 50% ustama bilan to'lanadi. Ortiqcha ish tungi vaqtga to'g'ri kelganda ikkala ustama bir vaqtda qo'llaniladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Ortiqcha ish to'lovi "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/jshshs","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"JShShS"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" 12% va ijtimoiy soliqqa umumiy asoslarda tortiladi — soliq bo'yicha imtiyozlar yo'q. Ish beruvchi har bir xodimning ortiqcha ish soatlarining aniq hisobini yuritishi shart. Ortiqcha ish davomiyligi normalari buzilganligi uchun mansabdor shaxslarga ma'muriy jarimalar nazarda tutilgan — 5 dan 10 "}],["$","$La","3",{"href":"/uz/calculator/bhm","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"BHK"}],["$","$1","4",{"children":"gacha (2 060 000 — 4 120 000 so'm)."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash misoli: oklad 10 000 000 so'm/oy, 168 ish soati. Soatlik stavka = 59 524 so'm. 4 soat ortiqcha ish: 2s × 89 286 (×1,5) + 2s × 119 048 (×2) = 416 668 so'm (oddiy stavkada 238 096 o'rniga). Ustama: 178 572 so'm. Dam olish kunida ish (8 soat): 8 × 119 048 = 952 384 so'm. Kalkulyatorimiz barcha ustamalar va soliqlarni hisobga olgan holda to'lovni hisoblaydi."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":["$L1a",["$L1b"]]}],"$L1c","$L1d"]}]
